                    <div class="comment-rating">★★★★★</div>
                </div>
                <div class="comment">
                    <div class="comment-author">Tawan</div>
                    <p>The Australian Wagyu beef from Lee Pot is incredibly tender, with beautiful marbling, that makes this meat juicy. It has a rich, intense flavor and a perfectly grilled aroma. Ideal for those who appreciate high-quality beef.</p>
                    <div class="comment-rating">★★★★★</div>
                </div>
                <div class="comment">
                    <div class="comment-author">Tawan</div>
                    <p>The Australian Wagyu beef from Lee Pot is incredibly tender, with beautiful marbling, that makes this meat juicy. It has a rich, intense flavor and a perfectly grilled aroma. Ideal for those who appreciate high-quality beef.</p>
                    <div class="comment-rating">★★★★★</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        
            <button class="accept-button" type="submit">
                <span>accept</span>
                <span></span>
            </button>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>